Package: vMF
Type: Package
Title: Sampling from von Mises-Fisher Distribution
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2019-09-02
Authors@R: person("Elysée Aristide", "Houndetoungan", role = c("cre","aut"), email =  "ariel92and@gmail.com")
Description: Provides fast sampling from von Mises-Fisher distribution use the method proposed by Andrew T.A Wood (1994) <doi:10.1080/03610919408813161>. Unlike 'movMF' of Kurt Hornik and Bettina Grün (2014) <doi:10.18637/jss.v058.i10> the mixtures on von Mises-Fisher distributions are not consider. However, fast sampling from the distribution are particularly regarded here. Advanced examples available 
\href{<https://ahoundetoungan.com/blog/2017/12/01/An-R-Package-for-Fast-Sampling-from-von-Mises-Fisher-Distribution.html>}{online} show how fast the sampling is and its usefulness.
